name: To submit a query in Query Portal and view its result sets in the Submitted Queries table

elements.name: Submitting a Query by selecting desired filter criteria

steps.name: User is on the OTQT Home Page.
User selects Date and Time range 10/02/2017 and 08:00:00 and 14:00:00 filters
User selects Types Orders And Trades and Equities Only filters
User selects Symbols AAPL filter
User inputs Exchanges ARCA filter
User inputs Order Id 16044086573117208 filter
User selects Order Types LMT filter
User inputs Trades Trade Price 153.40 and Trade Quantity 92 filters
User inputs Oder details 153.40 and 92 filters
User inputs Equity Capacity Principal filter
User clicks SUBMIT button
Submit Query Confirmation popup window is displayed

elements.name: Submit Query Confirmation popup window data validation

steps.name: User is on the Submit Query Confirmation popup window
User modifies the Query Name
User Validates the details of the Query Confirmation popup window
User clicks Submit button
The Submit Query Confirmation popup window is closed and the Submitted Query is listed in the Submitted Queries table grid
User validates the Query record data for all the columns for Statuses Processing and Completed
